00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:01.287
NATE BROOLING: So, hi, guys.

00:00:01.287 --> 00:00:02.328
My name is Nate Brooling.

00:00:02.328 --> 00:00:03.960
I sit across the
street over in sales,

00:00:03.960 --> 00:00:05.630
look after the
Microsoft business.

00:00:05.630 --> 00:00:07.600
So nice to meet you.

00:00:07.600 --> 00:00:10.410
We're here today because of a
good friend of mine, Erik Fay,

00:00:10.410 --> 00:00:12.800
was talking to me
about this fantastic

00:00:12.800 --> 00:00:17.810
story and this incredible woman
and team behind her as well.

00:00:17.810 --> 00:00:19.630
So he asked, you
know, hey, would

00:00:19.630 --> 00:00:22.130
