been incredible to me.

00:00:41.570 --> 00:00:43.670
And I cannot wait to see
what we're about to see.

00:00:43.670 --> 00:00:45.299
So I'm going to be quick.

00:00:45.299 --> 00:00:47.340
But before I bring her
up, a bit more about her--

00:00:47.340 --> 00:00:50.220
she holds a bachelor in
applied science, child studies,

00:00:50.220 --> 00:00:54.280
