and how to deal with
traffic jams in the brain."

00:01:41.580 --> 00:01:43.740
So I know a lot of us,
especially at Google, we

00:01:43.740 --> 00:01:48.440
have a lot of traffic
jams, sounds fitting.

00:01:48.440 --> 00:01:52.520
Her life has been a quest
to help individuals address

00:01:52.520 --> 00:01:54.650
learning difficulties
so they can

00:01:54.650 --> 00:01:57.100
experience the ease
and joy of learning

00:01:57.100 --> 00:01:59.650
as well as achieve their dreams.

00:01:59.650 --> 00:02:02.740
This program is
in over 91 schools

00:02:02.740 --> 00:02:07.010
across several countries,
Canada, USA, Australia, New

00:02:07.010 --> 00:02:09.226
Zealand, Malaysia,
